      "skill3": {
        "skillName": "Acclimatize",
        "stat": "int",
        "definition": "<p>When in a settlement a Bard can roll Acclimatize at a DC based on the settlement type. If successful, the Bard learns how to appear as a local and will no longer be treated as an outsider. This grants a +2 to Charisma &amp; Persuasion with locals and means that they won&rsquo;t be questioned or harassed like an outsider.</p>\n<ul>\n<li><strong>Hamlet:</strong> DC 25</li>\n<li><strong>Town:</strong> DC 20</li>\n<li><strong>City:</strong> DC 15</li>\n<li><strong>Capital:</strong> DC 10</li>\n</ul>",
